{"id":"524e2b7a-7be6-43b2-8f9d-0de202237a77","name":"Dragon Ball Z S.H. Figuarts Action Figure Cooler Final Form 19cm (Sealed box)","slug":"dragon-ball-z-s.h.-figuarts-action-figur-1-2-3-4-5-6","description":"<div><strong>Dragon Ball Z</strong> Action Figure of <strong>Cooler Final Form</strong> in<strong> S.H. Figuarts</strong> collection, size approx.19cm. <strong>Official product</strong> by <strong>Tamashii Nations.</strong><strong></strong></div>\n<div><strong></strong></div>\n<div>\"Well then... Ready to kneel?\"</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>Cooler</strong>, from the fifth movie, <strong>Dragon Ball Z: Cooler's Revenge</strong> joins <strong>S.H.Figuarts</strong>! He stands approx. 19cm tall. Exchangable hand parts, exchangable feet, and face part without his mask is included! Made by <strong>Tamashii Nations</strong>.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>Cooler</strong> is on the lookout for <strong>Son Goku</strong> not to avenge his brother <strong>Frieza</strong>, but to avenge the humiliation suffered by his family as a result of his being defeated by a Saiyan. Four henchmen face <strong>Son Gohan</strong>, <strong>Krillin</strong>, <strong>Son Goku</strong> and <strong>Piccolo</strong> but our heroes are quickly defeated. <strong>Goku</strong> recovered from a burn on his back thanks to a senzu set out in search of <strong>Cooler</strong>. <strong>Son Goku</strong> leads the fight and <strong>Cooler</strong>, in bad posture, transformed into his final form and gained the upper hand over his opponent who was unfortunately no match for him ...<br /><br />Set Contents:</div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>main body</li>\n<li>an optional expression part</li>\n<li>three pair of optional hand parts</li>\n<li>a pair of optional feet</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div><b></b></div>","metaTitle":null,"metaDescription":null,"model":null,"releaseDate":null,"image":null,"condition":null,"edition":null,"rarity":null,"features":null,"specifications":null,"createdAt":"2025-03-25T23:56:52.62